thread.title_full: Quality Logo Products, Inc. reviewed by Scott Smolinski

author: Scott Smolinski
title: Scott Smolinski
text: I feel the stress volleyballs are a fair value. They are good, and the speed at which I received them was awesome. I do feel that they are a bit overpriced for being blan, with no printing, but I would still order from here again.
